Air Bud 3 - World Pup [2000]

Not simply content with his basketball prowess, the hoop-shooting pooch sets his sights on soccer in this third installment. Soon enough, he's howling along with the U.S. Women's Soccer Team, playing with such notables as Brandi Chastain, Brianna Scurri, and Trisha Venturini. And this time out, Buddy also finds love, fathering a littler of lovable pups. And as if he didn't have enough to worry about with the championship game, he's got to save his little one from a gang of nefarious pup-nappers.
